      "text": [
        " طَوَافٌ فِي الْعَشْرِ أَفْضَلُ مِنْ سَبْعِينَ طَوَافاً فِي الْحَجِّ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ahmad Bin Muhammad, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from one of his companions, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘<span class=\"iTxt\">Tawaaf</span> during the tenth (of Zil Hijja) is superior than seventy <span class=\"iTxt\">Tawaaf</span>s during the Hajj’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "17. Ahmad ibn Muhammad has narrated from ibn abu ‘Umayr from certain persons of his people who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘Performing a Tawaf on tenth of Dhu al-Hajjah is more virtuous than seventy Tawaf during al-Hajj.’” "
        ]
      }
